Package agile.planner.scripter.tools

Class ScriptLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • agile.planner.scripter.tools.ScriptLog
  • public class ScriptLog
extends java.lang.Object
    One of the built-in tooling options that provides all relevant logging for the Simple scripting language. This involves providing a clear summary of all functions called, object instances created, and exceptions thrown when encountered.
